data.description: Fantastic home like new in a great neighborhood on a large lot. Home features new 2 tone paint, carpet, refinished hardwood floors all completed in Nov. 2016. Triple pane windows installed in June 2016.Garage opener and key pad new in 2016. Central air and 4 zone  Lenox furnace installed 2012. Oak cabinets, Stainless steel appliances, vaulted ceilings, oak railings, celling fans, all bathrooms and laundry room have tile floors. Private master suite, Master bath has large vanity, separate jetted tub and shower, large walk in closets. Large family room, lots of storage. Soft water. In ground trampoline, play gym, patio with pergola , basket ball court, vegetable grow boxes. Very private and shaded back yard great for family fun. Work bench and shelving in garage, RV parking with shed. Black fridge in garage can stay with the home. Call for a private showing. SQ. FT. from appraisal. SQ. FT. and all information to be verified by buyers
